1. Deck selection phase: .... decks listed from "decks" file
2. Print card phase:
- Title
- Front
- "Previous, Reveal, Next | <a> <s> <d>"
- User Input

if a -> clear screen then add "Back" to above

File of deck/card structure:
```
$title
$front
$back
$id
$previous
$next
```

Previous will contain the id of the previous card to be printed
analog with next.
